Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.95,0:00:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.50,0:00:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.64,0:00:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't know you were suffering this much...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.84,0:00:11.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But still...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.08,0:00:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's definitely a huge mistake to risk your life in this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.17,0:00:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't hold back anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.63,0:00:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll fight you with all my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And Mai, I'll find a way to make it so we can live like none of this ever happened between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.73,0:00:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sometime ago, for the sake of living, we left behind our happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.69,0:00:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We deceived ourselves, clinging to this mere illusion as we danced...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.99,0:01:02.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With closed eyes, at the end of the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.25,0:01:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was searching for your smiling face...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.71,0:01:16.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We embrace our dreams and continue on...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.72,0:01:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}within the swaying traces of memories...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.65,0:01:30.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Someday, I will once again grasp hold of
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.74,0:01:37.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}these feelings I have locked away in my heart... Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.46,0:02:00.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Revive! The Third Dragon"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.39,0:02:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't figure out a plan this turn,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.14,0:02:16.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi will lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.44,0:02:19.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the one who loses will have their souls sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.27,0:02:22.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to see that\N happen to Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} or Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.95,0:02:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Other Me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.57,0:02:28.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is there really nothing we can do?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.03,0:02:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Barrier of Orichalcos won't go away until one of their Life Points hits 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.29,0:02:36.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.29,0:02:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's also the key to saving them both.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.83,0:02:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} realizes it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.30,0:02:43.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And that is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.97,0:02:46.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many times he gets back up, it'll end the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.18,0:02:50.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just one more attack and Jounouchi's soul will belong to us of Doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:51.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Rafael?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:01.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I only have 200 Life Points...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.86,0:03:05.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even worse, Mai still has an untouched 4000...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The number of Monsters on the field is also in her favor...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.41,0:03:11.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even so, I can't give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.45,0:03:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As long as there's cards in\N my deck, there's a possibility!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.50,0:03:18.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's got to be a way to\N save me and Mai in this Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:21.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I could just destroy this boundary...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.09,0:03:24.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait! Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.30,0:03:26.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is all I can do...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.05,0:03:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll bet everything on this card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.76,0:03:35.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Magical Gigacyber to\N the field in Attack Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.88,0:03:37.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gigacyber?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.69,0:03:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a Six-Star Monster, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:45.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the opponent has at least two more Monsters than I do on the field, I can Special Summon him to the field without sacrificing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:51.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I use Gigacyber to attack Harpy Lady!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ye-yahh~!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:03.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At least he finally made a counterattack!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:04.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does Jounouchi seriously want to fight Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.66,0:04:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.30,0:04:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} has finally realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.43,0:04:14.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The way to end this Duel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.60,0:04:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If both of their Life Points hits 0 at the same time...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.64,0:04:21.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...the boundary may just disappear...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.04,0:04:24.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} has discovered this possibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.36,0:04:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Jounouchi fella's gotten pretty energetic all of a sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.07,0:04:29.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:31.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because he's a Chosen Duelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't change the fact that Mai will win.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.08,0:04:39.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I set one card in reverse! Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.75,0:04:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you're finally serious, Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.21,0:04:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.04,0:04:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm about as serious as I'll {\i1}ever{\i0} be!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.38,0:04:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This{\i0} is what I'm talking about...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.59,0:04:55.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To finally be able to move past this utter nonsense of friendship and fight you with all my might!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.81,0:04:57.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'll {\i1}win{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.27,0:05:01.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This place is...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.10,0:05:04.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't have to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.90,0:05:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your wishes will be fulfilled here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.48,0:05:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What exactly do you want me to do...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.49,0:05:13.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Welcome, Mai Kujaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.19,0:05:16.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To our temple of Doma.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.29,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And you are...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am Dartz.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.00,0:05:24.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The one who shall make your wish come true.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.29,0:05:27.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My.... wish...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.55,0:05:29.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your heart is trembling with fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.01,0:05:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Your fear is rooted in the despair and loneliness you tasted after suffering defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.51,0:05:41.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I am the only person capable of helping your heart let go of that fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.25,0:05:44.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}D-Don't speak nonsense...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.23,0:05:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.02,0:05:46.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm not...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:49.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...afraid of anything...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.48,0:05:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not afraid... of anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.57,0:05:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go! Winged Sun Dragon of Ra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.84,0:05:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}God Blaze Cannon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.74,0:06:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai Kujaku...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:07.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I plan on letting you enjoy the inside of the world in your mind to the {\b0}fullest{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.35,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.94,0:06:27.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:31.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't want to feel that ever again!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.24,0:06:34.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then all need you do is win.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.99,0:06:41.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Those who spoke trivial words of comfort to you in the past no longer stand beside you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will you continue to walk this maze all by yourself after having been left behind?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.58,0:06:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Or will you cease to follow in their tracks and get ahead of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.21,0:06:52.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is for you to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:56.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You did say you wanted to win, did you not, Mai Kujaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.73,0:06:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I {\b0}want{\b1} to win....!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.56,0:07:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For that purpose, are you prepared to throw everything else away?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.74,0:07:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to {\b0}win{\b1}!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.60,0:07:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to win! By {\b0}any{\b1} means!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.90,0:07:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Do you desire power for this purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.36,0:07:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.65,0:07:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Then I shall grant you it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.19,0:07:33.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}From this day forward, you will be one of us... of Doma!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.03,0:07:36.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.93,0:07:42.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With all the power I've mustered, Jounouchi, I'm going to {\i1}beat{\i0} you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.73,0:07:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why ya drivin' so fast...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.44,0:07:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I thought, this is strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.73,0:07:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The entire place is empty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.74,0:07:59.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Oi! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:00.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave us behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.95,0:08:03.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.99,0:08:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:08.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Otogi-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.54,0:08:11.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.83,0:08:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what {\i1}I{\i0} want to know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.88,0:08:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you Dueling in a place like {\i1}this{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} Dueling against Mai-{\i1}san{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't have time to explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.68,0:08:23.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something terrible happening!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been locked in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.43,0:08:27.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you open the door from out there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:28.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.52,0:08:29.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll try!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.98,0:08:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're counting on you, Otogi!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.61,0:08:36.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ryuzaki and Haga!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you guys here as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.32,0:08:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, that....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.24,0:08:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the boundary from that time!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.53,0:08:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.45,0:08:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We couldn't do a thing 'gainst that thing and we were done in!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:52.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sacrifice two Harpy Lady Copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.33,0:08:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Harpy's Pet Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.30,0:09:03.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Due to the effect of the Barrier of Orichalcos, its Attack goes up by 500!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for every Harpy Lady on the field,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.14,0:09:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it goes up another 300 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:13.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,3400 Attack Points?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.27,0:09:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That woman's horribly powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.86,0:09:19.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's so much different than she was back in the Duel Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:23.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did Mai Kujaku get that barrier card?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.24,0:09:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the last strike, Jounouchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.45,0:09:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Harpy's Pet Dragon!\NAttack Gigacyber!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.00,0:09:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card open!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.58,0:09:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Compensation Mediation!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.75,0:09:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card allows me to shuffle it with two cards from the opponent's Graveyard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.55,0:09:44.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can pick this card from the three cards,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,for this turn, all battles will be forced to a close.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.01,0:09:49.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:53.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance of getting your own card is one third!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.89,0:09:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he doesn't get it, he'll lose!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.51,0:09:58.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's seriously strugglin' right to the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.02,0:09:58.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.65,0:10:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he truly is one of the Duelists whose radiance shines brighter than all others,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.28,0:10:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he just might pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.52,0:10:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.69,0:10:10.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Choose two cards from your Graveyard, Mai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.08,0:10:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.87,0:10:17.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you shuffle them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.43,0:10:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, ready when you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.95,0:10:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, let me pick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:48.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I choose..... this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.97,0:11:04.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll choose.... this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:24.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yippeekayay!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.99,0:11:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bitchin'! He got it right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.70,0:11:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right on!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.74,0:11:30.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just {\i1}not possible{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.16,0:11:32.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His cheap good luck keeps getting better and better...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.77,0:11:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He really did it....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.27,0:11:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This turns' battle is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.51,0:11:44.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank goodness...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:46.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, he made it through this turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:49.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But compensation comes with a high price...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.22,0:11:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As expected of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.43,0:11:53.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you a hand for coming up with such a thorough plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However....
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.86,0:11:57.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:12:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opposing player gets to add the cards they chose to the top of their deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.32,0:12:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:08.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that means those cards are back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:11.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pharaoh Formation and Phoenix Formation...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.87,0:12:14.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter which she uses,\N they're both powerful cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.42,0:12:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,One of the two will be added to Mai's hand when she draws.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.68,0:12:22.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The battle may be over,\N but my turn isn't over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.05,0:12:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With the effect of the Orichalcos Barrier,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.22,0:12:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I move two Harpy Ladies to the back row!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.43,0:12:31.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I set two reverse cards face down! Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.23,0:12:36.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even though I avoided that attack earlier...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.35,0:12:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Gigacyber can't stand up to her strength....!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.02,0:12:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if Mai draws Phoenix Formation\N next turn, I'm finished....!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.82,0:12:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I still have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.28,0:12:49.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.62,0:12:52.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set one reverse card!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.87,0:12:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I Summon a Monster\N in face-down Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.67,0:12:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Gigacyber to Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.79,0:13:00.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.84,0:13:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Running on the defensive again, are we now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHUT UP! Shut yer trap!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.85,0:13:10.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not here either!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:14.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't hurry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.94,0:13:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.36,0:13:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:23.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.86,0:13:26.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It opened!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're awfully calm in this desperate situation, Jounouchi...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.06,0:13:37.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.53,0:13:39.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's one of the many lessons I learned in Battle City.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.88,0:13:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never give up until the last second, no matter what happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:45.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you do, a chance will come!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:46.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:50.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I was waiting for someone to save me then...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's why I have to win now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.22,0:13:53.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.60,0:13:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card open!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:58.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drop Off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.08,0:14:00.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.35,0:14:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let you have your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card open over here as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.94,0:14:06.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Jammer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I discard a card from my hand to make your Trap Card's activation useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:16.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.58,0:14:18.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which card did Mai draw...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.12,0:14:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You really have good luck...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll set this.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.30,0:14:27.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That card isn't Phoenix Formation! It's Pharaoh Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.95,0:14:30.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early to relax!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpy's Pet Dragon! Attack Gigacyber!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I use Harpy Lady to attack\N your Reverse Defense Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.20,0:14:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot diggity damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.82,0:14:53.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Reverse Effect of Fiber Pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:15:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Monsters on the field, our hands, and the cards in both our Graveyards return to the owners' decks, and then we shuffle them!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:02.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad at all, Jounouchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.13,0:15:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.09,0:15:06.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Reverse card open!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.80,0:15:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Harpy's Feather Snowstorm!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.39,0:15:20.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Card Effect can only be activated if my Harpy attacks! It makes all my enemy's Special Effects invalid!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.44,0:15:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi's Monsters were all destroyed again!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi....!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mai saw through all of Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}'s strategies....!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.70,0:15:34.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's strong...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.45,0:15:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn end!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.16,0:15:39.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now what'll you do next, Jounouchi?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Not yet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.25,0:15:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My Life isn't gone yet...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:45.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.13,0:15:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon a Monster in Face-down Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.59,0:15:52.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn over!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.51,0:15:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next turn, Mai will draw Phoenix Formation.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.89,0:16:01.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what Monster he played, he's done for with only 200 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn! Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.69,0:16:08.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's only one Monster left on Jounouchi's field...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.90,0:16:12.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If all my Harpy Ladies attack at once, I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.53,0:16:19.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But what if his Reverse Monster has a similar Effect to that Fiber Pot before...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.58,0:16:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}All I can do is use the magical effects of my Phoenix Formation to seal away his Special Abilities!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.58,0:16:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate a Magic Card from my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.75,0:16:29.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Phoenix Formation!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beat his Reverse Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.51,0:16:34.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I win!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.09,0:16:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.49,0:16:57.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi~!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.33,0:17:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-Neko Mane King?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.00,0:17:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.09,0:17:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Cat Mimicry King's Attack is 0!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.51,0:17:16.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So the effect of Phoenix Formation
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.65,0:17:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,that deducts half the destroyed Monster's Attack Points from the player's Life Points becomes meaningless!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.43,0:17:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, Neko Mane King's Special Effect is activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.44,0:17:34.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you send it to the Graveyard in this turn due to a Magic, Trap, or Monster Card Effect....
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.65,0:17:36.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the opponent's turn is forced to an end!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.32,0:17:39.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank God...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.53,0:17:42.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He barely made it by the skin of his teeth...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's got to be a limit to his strong good luck...!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:47.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This dude just doesn't know when to throw in the towel.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.62,0:17:50.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He just delayed his defeat for a single turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.38,0:17:51.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Knock it off already!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.95,0:17:55.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're still thinking about "saving me," you're more stupid than I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.68,0:17:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.68,0:18:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You know I'm bad at giving up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But that's Mai for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.47,0:18:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You don't give anyone time for a chance...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.10,0:18:09.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I can't think of a plan on the next draw...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.81,0:18:11.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll really lose for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.11,0:18:15.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will it end this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Will I lose before I save Mai, and before I beat these Doma punks a new one?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:22.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I won't accept that!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.91,0:18:25.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I can't give up yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.32,0:18:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm counting on you.... my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.04,0:18:30.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Any sort of miracle is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.29,0:18:32.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please give me a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.59,0:18:40.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.57,0:18:46.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The Monocle of Timaeus!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.35,0:18:47.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.57,0:18:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What's up with this light?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.36,0:19:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Fang of Critias?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:02.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the same as what happened to me before....!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.71,0:19:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Where is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.46,0:19:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mai? What happened to the Duel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.34,0:19:23.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the World of Duel Monsters!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.34,0:19:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The place where the Nameless Dragons sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.48,0:19:30.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This sword...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.43,0:19:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0}, only you can lift this sword!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.98,0:19:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one who can pull this sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.40,0:19:40.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the last one chosen by the Nameless Dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.57,0:19:41.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.25,0:19:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.29,0:19:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something spoke to me through this sword...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.59,0:20:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nameless Dragon...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:17.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know your name!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your name is... Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.62,0:20:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that just now? A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.50,0:20:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.66,0:20:34.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's right, Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1}....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.67,0:20:37.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've certainly been chosen\N by the Nameless Dragons...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.00,0:20:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What was....?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.96,0:20:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Big Brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:46.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, did you see the light just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.80,0:20:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, forget it then....
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Orichalcos is reacting....!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.07,0:20:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the power of the Nameless Dragons?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.97,0:21:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they trying to interfere again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.57,0:21:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What the hell just happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.20,0:21:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.82,0:21:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I don't know what just happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.74,0:21:11.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I can feel a power flowing through me...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.87,0:21:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll bet everything on this card!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.49,0:21:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Claw of Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.59,0:21:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Jounouchi now?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.71,0:21:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's acting stranger...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:25.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.34,0:21:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like we thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.30,0:21:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Jounouchi-{\i0}kun{\i1} is the last to be chosen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.18,0:21:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.26,0:21:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as he has that card...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.43,0:21:37.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you.... Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.40,0:21:40.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please lend me your power!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:22:02.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The houses lined down the street drifting by being dyed red
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.31,0:22:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I notice pain, it'll turn into happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.92,0:22:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Every time people wipe away tears, they understand bonds
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.99,0:22:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The warm strength that you gave me will change into kindness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.47,0:22:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Overflowing feelings don't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.75,0:22:51.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'll live while I feel it, for me to be myself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.65,0:23:00.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Healed by overflowing friendship
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.80,0:23:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our fated encounter is a truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.32,0:23:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and someday we'll be able to understand each other
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.51,0:23:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi got a special card when he was in a desperate situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.59,0:23:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.18,0:23:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like Yugi was entrusted with a Legendary Dragon Card from the Duel Monsters world,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.06,0:23:32.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jounouchi was chosen by that card too!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.35,0:23:35.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Nameless Dragon - The Claw of Hermos!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:41.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could this card's hidden power be enough to save Jounouchi and Mai-{\i1}san{\i0} from this Duel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.87,0:23:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time: {\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&H000000&}"The Miracle of Hermos"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
